id  ,
type  ,

extra_css  ,

) [inline, private]

Erstellt ein neues DomTreeObject und hängt es beim angegebenen Parent ein.

Returns:
: newDomTreeObject or null if error occurs returned DomTreeObject saves parent in nextNode
Defintions:
: HTML Objecttag: nextNode is reserved to save Wrapper Elements
Parameters:
 parent Element Element where the new Element should add to
 id string id of the ne HTML Object
 type string HTML-Type of the new DomTreeObject. Default: div
 css string normal css class. Default: "NOTSET"
 extra_css string secoond css class. Default: "EXTRA_NOTSET"
 src string for HTML types that need a sourcePath like img. Default: ""
